00:00:53.560 --> 00:00:54.719
How can you treat it so lightly?

00:00:55.159 --> 00:00:57.119
You hold the title of Princess Royal.

00:00:57.719 --> 00:00:59.759
You should bless the people.

00:01:00.159 --> 00:01:01.359
You must not shirk this duty.

00:01:03.880 --> 00:01:04.599
Yes.

00:01:04.599 --> 00:01:05.719
I will obey your command.

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:07.799
Princess Er,

00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:11.879
Princess Royal knows little of the festival's details.

00:01:12.359 --> 00:01:13.560
Starting tomorrow,

00:01:13.879 --> 00:01:15.959
