00:01:16.599 --> 00:01:17.920
Be thorough and precise.

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:19.480
No mistakes are allowed.

00:01:21.560 --> 00:01:22.159
Yes.

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:22.920
Empress Mother,

00:01:23.200 --> 00:01:25.239
I will do my best to assist my sister.

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:27.480
We'll organize the Festival of Ingenuity well.

00:01:35.879 --> 00:01:37.359
Greetings, Princess.

00:01:38.599 --> 00:01:39.599
Hello, Sister.

00:01:40.879 --> 00:01:42.000
What are you two doing?

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:46.200
Who drank this water?

00:01:46.319 --> 00:01:47.280
It smells bad now.

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:52.040
Sister,

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:53.959
On the fifth of the seventh month,

00:01:54.079 --> 00:01:56.599
the Festival of Ingenuity features the Needle-Floating Skill Test.

00:01:56.959 --> 00:01:58.959
Women place bowls of water in the sun.

00:01:59.239 --> 00:02:00.159
After a while,

00:02:00.159 --> 00:02:01.280
a film forms on the water's surface.

00:02:01.599 --> 00:02:02.560
This embroidery needle,

00:02:02.560 --> 00:02:03.799
when dropped in, will float.

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:05.799
Look at the shadow on the water's bottom.

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:09.199
If it forms shapes of clouds, flowers, birds, or beasts,

00:02:09.439 --> 00:02:10.599
Enough, enough, enough!

00:02:10.680 --> 00:02:11.759
Stop with the fancy talk.

00:02:11.759 --> 00:02:12.560
I don't like listening to it.

00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:18.919
Threading needles, year after year, with neighbors.

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:22.120
Testing one's skill and spirit with the needle.

00:02:22.759 --> 00:02:24.960
Who alone sees the shadow of the dragon shuttle?

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:27.400
Embroidering mandarin ducks, yet not crossing paths.

00:02:28.280 --> 00:02:29.360
Needle-Floating Skill Test.

00:02:29.759 --> 00:02:31.560
It seeks not only skillful hands,

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:35.719
but also a perfect match in secret.

00:02:36.199 --> 00:02:38.080
What are you two talking about?

00:02:38.080 --> 00:02:39.159
I have no idea what you're saying.

00:02:40.080 --> 00:02:40.879
But

00:02:41.080 --> 00:02:42.800
this perfect match

00:02:42.800 --> 00:02:44.719
sounds rather interesting to me.

00:02:49.599 --> 00:02:51.879
Why are there needles stuck in this potato?

00:02:52.960 --> 00:02:53.960
On the night of the Festival,

00:02:53.960 --> 00:02:55.120
one must face the moon

00:02:55.120 --> 00:02:56.560
and thread needles continuously.

00:02:56.960 --> 00:02:59.159
Whoever threads fastest is deemed skillful.

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:01.680
She becomes this year's clever maiden.

00:03:12.759 --> 00:03:14.039
That's impressive.

00:03:15.879 --> 00:03:17.800
What's the point, really?

00:03:18.360 --> 00:03:19.800
All these pointless things.

00:03:24.919 --> 00:03:25.520
Little Yuanyuan,

00:03:25.520 --> 00:03:25.960
