00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:31.080
Give me your hand.

00:03:31.879 --> 00:03:32.680
What for?

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:34.479
To dye your fingernails.

00:03:35.080 --> 00:03:36.039
Dyeing fingernails?

00:03:36.039 --> 00:03:36.919
That's right.

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:38.960
