00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:29.360
Please don't hold it against her.

00:04:31.199 --> 00:04:33.160
Princess Er is always gentle and wise.

00:04:33.319 --> 00:04:34.279
She truly understands people.

00:04:44.399 --> 00:04:45.079
Little Yuanyuan,

00:04:45.160 --> 00:04:45.800
Princess,

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:46.759
