00:04:55.279 --> 00:04:57.600
I didn't expect you to be so thoughtful.

00:04:58.759 --> 00:04:59.759
Actually,

00:04:59.959 --> 00:05:02.160
I've been thinking a lot lately.

00:05:03.199 --> 00:05:05.279
